<p data-start="186" data-end="287">👉 You just type a product name<br data-start="217" data-end="220">
👉 And instantly generate a <strong data-start="248" data-end="287">high-quality, accurate image prompt</strong></p>
<hr data-start="289" data-end="292">
<h1 data-section-id="7dakme" data-start="294" data-end="348">🔍 1. What Your Dataset Already Has (Very Strong 👍)</h1>
<p data-start="350" data-end="449">Your dataset is actually <strong data-start="375" data-end="399">perfectly structured</strong> for AI image generation. Key columns that matter:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1oawgqq" data-start="451" data-end="478">🎯 Visual Design Fields</h3>
<ul data-start="479" data-end="609">
<li data-section-id="9yzjhg" data-start="479" data-end="494">
<p data-start="481" data-end="494"><code data-start="481" data-end="494">productName</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1u0nnug" data-start="495" data-end="507">
<p data-start="497" data-end="507"><code data-start="497" data-end="507">category</code></p>
</li>
