<p data-start="888" data-end="953">👉 This is MORE than enough to generate realistic product images.</p>
<hr data-start="955" data-end="958">
<h1 data-section-id="v90exy" data-start="960" data-end="1012">⚠️ 2. What Was Missing (Now I’m Fixing It for You)</h1>
<p data-start="1014" data-end="1052">To generate images properly, AI needs:</p>
<ul data-start="1054" data-end="1149">
<li data-section-id="17nxd8u" data-start="1054" data-end="1086">
<p data-start="1056" data-end="1086">Scene context (indoor/outdoor)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1r72oih" data-start="1087" data-end="1123">
<p data-start="1089" data-end="1123">Style (modern, industrial, luxury)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="oy92s0" data-start="1124" data-end="1138">
<p data-start="1126" data-end="1138">Camera angle</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ltr4ja" data-start="1139" data-end="1149">
<p data-start="1141" data-end="1149">Lighting</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1151" data-end="1241">👉 Your dataset doesn’t explicitly store these — but we can <strong data-start="1211" data-end="1240">derive them automatically</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1243" data-end="1246">
<h1 data-section-id="1it59mn" data-start="1248" data-end="1298">🧠 3. Smart Logic to Convert Data → Image Prompt</h1>
<p data-start="1300" data-end="1336">Here’s how your system should think:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="g9f342" data-start="1338" data-end="1356">Example Input:</h3>
<p data-start="1357" data-end="1428"><strong data-start="1357" data-end="1374">Product Name:</strong><br data-start="1374" data-end="1377">
<code data-start="1377" data-end="1428">Modular Brushed Balcony Railing with Glass Infill</code></p>
<hr data-start="1430" data-end="1433">
<h3 data-section-id="1ekdxz3" data-start="1435" data-end="1466">🧩 Step 1: Extract Row Data</h3>
<p data-start="1467" data-end="1480">From dataset:</p>
<ul data-start="1481" data-end="1626">
<li data-section-id="k0nb3y" data-start="1481" data-end="1519">
<p data-start="1483" data-end="1519">furnitureType → Wall Mounted Railing</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="118doab" data-start="1520" data-end="1556">
<p data-start="1522" data-end="1556">material → Stainless Steel + Glass</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sv00ly" data-start="1557" data-end="1575">
<p data-start="1559" data-end="1575">finish → Brushed</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="g00mxc" data-start="1576" data-end="1594">
<p data-start="1578" data-end="1594">color → Metallic</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="151byob" data-start="1595" data-end="1626">
<p data-start="1597" data-end="1626">usageArea → Balcony / Outdoor</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1628" data-end="1631">
<h3 data-section-id="e1ut6r" data-start="1633" data-end="1665">🧩 Step 2: Convert to Prompt</h3>
<h3 data-section-id="1leevt3" data-start="1667" data-end="1697">🔥 FINAL AI PROMPT FORMAT:</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1698" data-end="2387"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ftjksuqy.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>A high-quality realistic product render of a {productName}, </span><br><span>featuring {frameMaterial} structure with {surfaceFinish} finish, </span><br><span>and {enclosureMaterial/topMaterial} elements.</span><br><br><span>The product is designed as a {furnitureType} used in {usageArea}, </span><br><span>with a modern industrial aesthetic.</span><br><br><span>Dimensions are approximately {length}cm x {width}cm x {height}cm, </span><br><span>showing sturdy construction with {steelGrade} steel.</span><br><br><span>Scene: Installed in a realistic {usageArea} environment (e.g., balcony/home/office), </span><br><span>with natural lighting, clean background, and premium architectural setting.</span><br><br><span>Camera angle: Slight perspective front view, focusing on material details.</span><br><br><span>Highly detailed, photorealistic, 4K render.</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2389" data-end="2392">
<h1 data-section-id="1f05dej" data-start="2394" data-end="2434">⚡ 4. Your Exact Use Case (AUTO SYSTEM)</h1>
<p data-start="2436" data-end="2459">You can implement this:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="48b5n3" data-start="2461" data-end="2479">👉 User Input:</h3>
