<h1 data-section-id="1gavzg4" data-start="2629" data-end="2678">💡 5. Example Generated Prompt (From Your Data)</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2680" data-end="3348"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ftjksuqy.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>A high-quality realistic product render of a Modular Brushed Balcony Railing with Glass Infill, </span><br><span>featuring stainless steel structure with brushed finish, </span><br><span>and transparent glass infill panels.</span><br><br><span>The product is designed as a wall mounted railing used in residential balcony areas, </span><br><span>with a modern industrial aesthetic.</span><br><br><span>The structure shows durable steel grade construction with strong load-bearing capacity.</span><br><br><span>Scene: Installed in a modern balcony setting with outdoor greenery, </span><br><span>natural daylight, and clean architectural background.</span><br><br><span>Camera angle: Slight angled front perspective highlighting the glass and steel joints.</span><br><br><span>Highly detailed, photorealistic, 4K render.</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="3350" data-end="3353">
<h1 data-section-id="1tdg22b" data-start="3355" data-end="3404">🚀 6. Upgrade (VERY IMPORTANT for Your Project)</h1>
<p data-start="3406" data-end="3462">To make your system <strong data-start="3426" data-end="3461">next-level (like Amazon / IKEA)</strong>:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="uxqt0" data-start="3464" data-end="3523">Add these computed fields (don’t change original data):</h3>
<ul data-start="3525" data-end="3831">
<li data-section-id="tvguf" data-start="3525" data-end="3665">
<p data-start="3527" data-end="3562"><code data-start="3527" data-end="3538">sceneType</code> → auto from usageArea</p>
<ul data-start="3565" data-end="3665">
<li data-section-id="1wn7rwm" data-start="3565" data-end="3598">
<p data-start="3567" data-end="3598">balcony → outdoor modern home</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ks1jdc" data-start="3601" data-end="3631">
<p data-start="3603" data-end="3631">hospital → clinical indoor</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ekqax" data-start="3634" data-end="3665">
<p data-start="3636" data-end="3665">office → corporate interior</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8ub73i" data-start="3667" data-end="3746">
<p data-start="3669" data-end="3693"><code data-start="3669" data-end="3679">styleTag</code> → from tags</p>
<ul data-start="3696" data-end="3746">
<li data-section-id="8qc8ll" data-start="3696" data-end="3716">
<p data-start="3698" data-end="3716">modular → modern</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5r1ojz" data-start="3719" data-end="3746">
<p data-start="3721" data-end="3746">heavy-duty → industrial</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1u83doc" data-start="3748" data-end="3831">
<p data-start="3750" data-end="3772"><code data-start="3750" data-end="3760">lighting</code> → default</p>
<ul data-start="3775" data-end="3831">
<li data-section-id="1cmcp7m" data-start="3775" data-end="3798">
<p data-start="3777" data-end="3798">indoor → soft white</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ft126p" data-start="3801" data-end="3831">
<p data-start="3803" data-end="3831">outdoor → natural daylight</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
