<p data-start="54" data-end="182">👉 You don’t just want <strong data-start="77" data-end="95">product images</strong><br data-start="95" data-end="98">
👉 You want <strong data-start="110" data-end="156">professional product specification visuals</strong> like the one you shared</p>
<p data-start="184" data-end="263">This is <strong data-start="192" data-end="259">next-level catalog rendering (like IKEA / industrial brochures)</strong> ✅</p>
<hr data-start="265" data-end="268">
<h1 data-section-id="w7uhdl" data-start="270" data-end="298">🎯 What You Want (Decoded)</h1>
<p data-start="300" data-end="360">From your sample image, each generated image should include:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="laq2oo" data-start="362" data-end="391">✅ 1. Clean Product Render</h3>
<ul data-start="392" data-end="471">
<li data-section-id="gg4yt8" data-start="392" data-end="423">
<p data-start="394" data-end="423">Plain background (white/grey)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="mmv3s8" data-start="424" data-end="448">
<p data-start="426" data-end="448">Center-focused product</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1xvzhoe" data-start="449" data-end="471">
<p data-start="451" data-end="471">Slight 3D angle view</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="5kk8mn" data-start="473" data-end="495">✅ 2. Brand + Title</h3>
<ul data-start="496" data-end="570">
<li data-section-id="12ddg0v" data-start="496" data-end="533">
<p data-start="498" data-end="533">Top Left: <strong data-start="508" data-end="533">ShriKrishnaSteelWorks</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="jebv8x" data-start="534" data-end="570">
<p data-start="536" data-end="570">Top Center/Right: <strong data-start="554" data-end="570">Product Name</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="1drwumk" data-start="572" data-end="613">✅ 3. Dimension Lines (VERY IMPORTANT)</h3>
<ul data-start="614" data-end="687">
<li data-section-id="16y5c0" data-start="614" data-end="639">
<p data-start="616" data-end="639">Length (horizontal top)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1cvi0st" data-start="640" data-end="662">
<p data-start="642" data-end="662">Width (depth bottom)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uzvvgf" data-start="663" data-end="687">
<p data-start="665" data-end="687">Height (vertical side)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="1l07mxn" data-start="689" data-end="728">✅ 4. Feature Callouts (with arrows)</h3>
<p data-start="729" data-end="734">Like:</p>
<ul data-start="735" data-end="814">
<li data-section-id="pc0sii" data-start="735" data-end="756">
<p data-start="737" data-end="756">Mild steel tabletop</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="l4k1oc" data-start="757" data-end="779">
<p data-start="759" data-end="779">Galvanized structure</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1xt7v9u" data-start="780" data-end="796">
<p data-start="782" data-end="796">Pipe thickness</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1skngkn" data-start="797" data-end="814">
<p data-start="799" data-end="814">Storage cabinet</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="l0kod4" data-start="816" data-end="861">✅ 5. Model Number (Optional but powerful)</h3>
<ul data-start="862" data-end="881">
<li data-section-id="1wwqsnd" data-start="862" data-end="881">
<p data-start="864" data-end="881">e.g. SKSW-SF-9201</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="883" data-end="886">
<h1 data-section-id="1pka0ux" data-start="888" data-end="934">🧠 How We Convert Your Dataset → This Format</h1>
<p data-start="936" data-end="967">For every product, we generate:</p>
<h2 data-section-id="jd485e" data-start="969" data-end="996">🧩 1. Dimensions Mapping</h2>
<p data-start="997" data-end="1010">From dataset:</p>
<ul data-start="1011" data-end="1114">
<li data-section-id="241vxo" data-start="1011" data-end="1046">
<p data-start="1013" data-end="1046"><code data-start="1013" data-end="1024">length_cm</code> → Top horizontal line</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ecd0td" data-start="1047" data-end="1079">
<p data-start="1049" data-end="1079"><code data-start="1049" data-end="1059">width_cm</code> → Bottom depth line</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="e7f7gz" data-start="1080" data-end="1114">
<p data-start="1082" data-end="1114"><code data-start="1082" data-end="1093">height_cm</code> → Side vertical line</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1116" data-end="1119">
<h2 data-section-id="14bizgf" data-start="1121" data-end="1148">🧩 2. Feature Extraction</h2>
<p data-start="1149" data-end="1154">From:</p>
<ul data-start="1155" data-end="1235">
<li data-section-id="xibs6n" data-start="1155" data-end="1167">
<p data-start="1157" data-end="1167"><code data-start="1157" data-end="1167">features</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17iztr2" data-start="1168" data-end="1185">
<p data-start="1170" data-end="1185"><code data-start="1170" data-end="1185">frameMaterial</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="110u5ag" data-start="1186" data-end="1201">
<p data-start="1188" data-end="1201"><code data-start="1188" data-end="1201">topMaterial</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5jvf12" data-start="1202" data-end="1216">
<p data-start="1204" data-end="1216"><code data-start="1204" data-end="1216">steelGrade</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1kq0iub" data-start="1217" data-end="1235">
<p data-start="1219" data-end="1235"><code data-start="1219" data-end="1235">frameThickness</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1237" data-end="1265">👉 Convert into labels like:</p>
<ul data-start="1266" data-end="1375">
<li data-section-id="miwam8" data-start="1266" data-end="1307">
<p data-start="1268" data-end="1307">“High-grade galvanized steel structure”</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1iu0ts9" data-start="1308" data-end="1344">
<p data-start="1310" data-end="1344">“Round pipe frame – 6mm thickness”</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="106b0ms" data-start="1345" data-end="1375">
<p data-start="1347" data-end="1375">“Heavy-duty storage cabinet”</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1377" data-end="1380">
<h2 data-section-id="dbhzmf" data-start="1382" data-end="1427">🧩 3. Visual Style Prompt (VERY IMPORTANT)</h2>
<p data-start="1429" data-end="1460">Use THIS exact prompt format 👇</p>
<hr data-start="1462" data-end="1465">
<h1 data-section-id="rsjppr" data-start="1467" data-end="1509">🔥 MASTER IMAGE PROMPT (FOR YOUR SYSTEM)</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1511" data-end="2438"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ftjksuqy.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>A professional industrial product catalog image of {productName} by ShriKrishnaSteelWorks.</span><br><br><span>The product is a {furnitureType} made of {frameMaterial} with {surfaceFinish} finish, designed for {usageArea} use.</span><br><br><span>The product is displayed on a clean white background in a 3D perspective view.</span><br><br><span>Include technical dimension lines:</span><br><span>- Length: {length_cm} cm (top horizontal)</span><br><span>- Width: {width_cm} cm (bottom depth)</span><br><span>- Height: {height_cm} cm (vertical side)</span><br><br><span>Add annotated feature callouts with arrows pointing to parts:</span><br><span>- {feature1}</span><br><span>- {feature2}</span><br><span>- {feature3}</span><br><span>- {feature4}</span><br><br><span>Include branding text "ShriKrishnaSteelWorks" at top left.</span><br><br><span>Display product title "{productName}" at top.</span><br><br><span>Optional: Add model number {productId} near the product.</span><br><br><span>Style: minimal, engineering catalog, monochrome theme, high clarity, precise labeling, professional manufacturing brochure style.</span><br><br><span>Highly detailed, sharp, technical, 4K render.</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2440" data-end="2443">
