><br><span>- Round pipe frame – 6mm thickness</span><br><span>- Lockable storage cabinet</span><br><br><span>Style: engineering catalog, clean, technical, professional.</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
