The generated image looks more like a <strong data-start="93" data-end="114">table/workstation</strong>, not a proper <strong data-start="129" data-end="148">kitchen trolley</strong> ❌</p>
<p data-start="154" data-end="180">Let’s fix this properly 👇</p>
<hr data-start="182" data-end="185">
<h1 data-section-id="ivyhpn" data-start="187" data-end="206">❌ What Went Wrong</h1>
<p data-start="207" data-end="228">The AI misunderstood:</p>
<ul data-start="229" data-end="336">
<li data-section-id="1alc2mw" data-start="229" data-end="264">
<p data-start="231" data-end="264">❌ Made it like a <strong data-start="248" data-end="264">static table</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="75jqg4" data-start="265" data-end="300">
<p data-start="267" data-end="300">❌ Structure looks bulky and wrong</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1x50xw6" data-start="301" data-end="336">
<p data-start="303" data-end="336">❌ Trolley functionality not clear</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="338" data-end="341">
<h1 data-section-id="1alkbbo" data-start="343" data-end="391">✅ What a REAL Kitchen Trolley Should Look Like</h1>
<p data-start="393" data-end="464">A correct <strong data-start="403" data-end="451">Catering SS 304 Kitchen Trolley with Drawers</strong> should have:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="y9jtcz" data-start="466" data-end="489">🔧 Proper Structure</h3>
<ul data-start="490" data-end="587">
<li data-section-id="13j0wb1" data-start="490" data-end="520">
<p data-start="492" data-end="520">Slim stainless steel frame</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="n65x4t" data-start="521" data-end="560">
<p data-start="523" data-end="560">Open design (not closed like table)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1k3fnz9" data-start="561" data-end="587">
<p data-start="563" data-end="587">Clear trolley mobility</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="1mjpul6" data-start="589" data-end="619">🛞 Wheels (VERY IMPORTANT)</h3>
<ul data-start="620" data-end="686">
<li data-section-id="nkl5m6" data-start="620" data-end="639">
<p data-start="622" data-end="639">4 caster wheels</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="19lns5q" data-start="640" data-end="666">
<p data-start="642" data-end="666">At least 2 with brakes</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="pp6l3e" data-start="667" data-end="686">
<p data-start="669" data-end="686">Clearly visible</p>
