<p data-start="63" data-end="180">You want <strong data-start="72" data-end="96">ALL generated images</strong> to follow a <strong data-start="109" data-end="147">STANDARD INDUSTRIAL CATALOG FORMAT</strong> like your first reference image.</p>
<hr data-start="182" data-end="185">
<h1 data-section-id="1sbh9js" data-start="187" data-end="239">✅ FINAL STANDARD FORMAT (YOU WANT FOR EVERY IMAGE)</h1>
<p data-start="241" data-end="266">Every image MUST include:</p>
<hr data-start="268" data-end="271">
<h2 data-section-id="1rylpe4" data-start="273" data-end="296">🧾 1. HEADER SECTION</h2>
<ul data-start="297" data-end="376">
<li data-section-id="oz9yl0" data-start="297" data-end="330">
<p data-start="299" data-end="330">Left: <strong data-start="305" data-end="330">ShriKrishnaSteelWorks</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3yvy44" data-start="331" data-end="376">
<p data-start="333" data-end="376">Right/Center: <strong data-start="347" data-end="376">Product Name (BIG &amp; BOLD)</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="378" data-end="381">
<h2 data-section-id="wi4u6r" data-start="383" data-end="407">📦 2. PRODUCT DISPLAY</h2>
<ul data-start="408" data-end="525">
<li data-section-id="1eejbrr" data-start="408" data-end="426">
<p data-start="410" data-end="426">Only <strong data-start="415" data-end="426">product</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15obns3" data-start="427" data-end="468">
<p data-start="429" data-end="468">Plain <strong data-start="435" data-end="468">white / light grey background</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1a96p0h" data-start="469" data-end="497">
<p data-start="471" data-end="497">No room / no environment ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1c2e2be" data-start="498" data-end="525">
<p data-start="500" data-end="525">Slight <strong data-start="507" data-end="525">3D angled view</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="527" data-end="530">
<h2 data-section-id="rcw9nj" data-start="532" data-end="563">📏 3. DIMENSIONS (MANDATORY)</h2>
<p data-start="565" data-end="598">Always include 3 main dimensions:</p>
<ul data-start="600" data-end="707">
<li data-section-id="1d5mr2w" data-start="600" data-end="639">
<p data-start="602" data-end="639"><strong data-start="602" data-end="617">Length (cm)</strong> → bottom horizontal</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sv9qit" data-start="640" data-end="671">
<p data-start="642" data-end="671"><strong data-start="642" data-end="656">Width (cm)</strong> → depth side</p>
</li>
