<p data-start="145" data-end="210">No confusion from now — this is your <strong data-start="182" data-end="207">fixed template system</strong> 👇</p>
<hr data-start="212" data-end="215">
<h1 data-section-id="b2dnf4" data-start="217" data-end="260">🔥 YOUR FINAL IMAGE FORMAT (STRICT RULES)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1oapjn5" data-start="262" data-end="280">✅ 1. BACKGROUND</h2>
<ul data-start="281" data-end="385">
<li data-section-id="1c1v98t" data-start="281" data-end="311">
<p data-start="283" data-end="311">Plain <strong data-start="289" data-end="311">white / light grey</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ae9uqi" data-start="312" data-end="353">
<p data-start="314" data-end="353">No environment, no room, no scenery ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1wvulpy" data-start="354" data-end="385">
<p data-start="356" data-end="385">Clean <strong data-start="362" data-end="385">studio product shot</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="387" data-end="390">
<h2 data-section-id="v5k7vt" data-start="392" data-end="412">✅ 2. HEADER (TOP)</h2>
<ul data-start="413" data-end="502">
<li data-section-id="193hp4k" data-start="413" data-end="448">
<p data-start="415" data-end="448"><strong data-start="415" data-end="424">Left:</strong> <code data-start="425" data-end="448">ShriKrishnaSteelWorks</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="f2r02a" data-start="449" data-end="502">
<p data-start="451" data-end="502"><strong data-start="451" data-end="470">Right / Center:</strong> <code data-start="471" data-end="502">PRODUCT NAME (ALL CAPS, BOLD)</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="504" data-end="507">
<h2 data-section-id="1vfgx0b" data-start="509" data-end="529">✅ 3. PRODUCT VIEW</h2>
<ul data-start="530" data-end="663">
<li data-section-id="ai4zjh" data-start="530" data-end="553">
<p data-start="532" data-end="553">Single product only</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1gk71sg" data-start="554" data-end="600">
<p data-start="556" data-end="600">Slight <strong data-start="563" data-end="598">3D angled view (not flat front)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="uca5zj" data-start="601" data-end="619">
<p data-start="603" data-end="619">Center aligned</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ud5t76" data-start="620" data-end="663">
<p data-start="622" data-end="663">No extra objects unless part of product</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="665" data-end="668">
<h2 data-section-id="143wicn" data-start="670" data-end="701">✅ 4. DIMENSIONS (COMPULSORY)</h2>
<p data-start="703" data-end="736">Always show 3 arrows with labels:</p>
<ul data-start="738" data-end="834">
<li data-section-id="1uy4tet" data-start="738" data-end="775">
<p data-start="740" data-end="775">📏 <strong data-start="743" data-end="753">Length</strong> → bottom horizontal</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1132x2w" data-start="776" data-end="805">
<p data-start="778" data-end="805">📏 <strong data-start="781" data-end="790">Width</strong> → side depth</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ddk65h" data-start="806" data-end="834">
<p data-start="808" data-end="834">📏 <strong data-start="811" data-end="821">Height</strong> → vertical</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="836" data-end="854">👉 Format example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="855" data-end="885"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ftjksuqy.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>120 cm   60 cm   95 cm</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="887" data-end="935">👉 With <strong data-start="895" data-end="935">arrow lines like engineering drawing</strong></p>
<hr data-start="937" data-end="940">
<h2 data-section-id="pq6o0c" data-start="942" data-end="981">✅ 5. FEATURE CALLOUTS (LEFT &amp; RIGHT)</h2>
<p data-start="983" data-end="1023">Use arrows pointing to parts of product:</p>
<p data-start="1025" data-end="1040">Example format:</p>
<ul data-start="1041" data-end="1149">
<li data-section-id="1eb3k85" data-start="1041" data-end="1078">
<p data-start="1043" data-end="1078">Premium stainless steel structure</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="195y0rr" data-start="1079" data-end="1099">
<p data-start="1081" data-end="1099">Heavy-duty frame</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xx1to8" data-start="1100" data-end="1124">
<p data-start="1102" data-end="1124">Smooth caster wheels</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1mu6jwm" data-start="1125" data-end="1149">
<p data-start="1127" data-end="1149">Storage compartments</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1151" data-end="1190">👉 Max: 4–5 points (clean, not crowded)</p>
<hr data-start="1192" data-end="1195">
<h2 data-section-id="1wzhfsq" data-start="1197" data-end="1232">✅ 6. MODEL NUMBER (BOTTOM RIGHT)</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1234" data-end="1258"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ftjksuqy.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Model: SKSW-XXXX</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1260" data-end="1263">
<h2 data-section-id="mv84ry" data-start="1265" data-end="1278">✅ 7. STYLE</h2>
<ul data-start="1280" data-end="1383">
<li data-section-id="55wl6z" data-start="1280" data-end="1291">
<p data-start="1282" data-end="1291">Minimal</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1xd9hnz" data-start="1292" data-end="1306">
<p data-start="1294" data-end="1306">Industrial</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="f97pad" data-start="1307" data-end="1335">
<p data-start="1309" data-end="1335">Engineering catalog look</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12omfey" data-start="1336" data-end="1356">
<p data-start="1338" data-end="1356">Clean typography</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="rqxhzb" data-start="1357" data-end="1383">
<p data-start="1359" data-end="1383">High clarity (4K look)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1385" data-end="1388">
<h1 data-section-id="10y91i5" data-start="1390" data-end="1426">⚠️ COMMON MISTAKES (NEVER DO THIS)</h1>
<p data-start="1428" data-end="1599">❌ No bedroom / kitchen / balcony background<br data-start="1471" data-end="1474">
❌ No extra decoration (plants, people, etc.)<br data-start="1518" data-end="1521">
❌ No wrong product shape<br data-start="1545" data-end="1548">
❌ No mixed product types<br data-start="1572" data-end="1575">
❌ No over-crowded text</p>
<hr data-start="1601" data-end="1604">
<h1 data-section-id="emo68q" data-start="1606" data-end="1648">🚀 FINAL MASTER PROMPT (USE THIS ALWAYS)</h1>
<p data-start="1650" data-end="1672">Copy this and reuse 👇</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1674" data-end="2497"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ftjksuqy.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>A professional industrial product catalog image of {productName} by ShriKrishnaSteelWorks.</span><br><br><span>Display only the product on a clean white background with no environment.</span><br><br><span>The product is a {furnitureType} made of {material} with a modern industrial design.</span><br><br><span>Show the product in a slight 3D angled perspective view.</span><br><br><span>Add technical dimension lines with arrows:</span><br><span>- Length: {length_cm} cm (bottom)</span><br><span>- Width: {width_cm} cm (side)</span><br><span>- Height: {height_cm} cm (vertical)</span><br><br><span>Add feature callouts with arrows pointing to parts:</span><br><span>- {feature1}</span><br><span>- {feature2}</span><br><span>- {feature3}</span><br><span>- {feature4}</span><br><br><span>Include branding "ShriKrishnaSteelWorks" at top left.</span><br><br><span>Display product title "{productName}" at top.</span><br><br><span>Add model number "Model: {productId}" at bottom right.</span><br><br><span>Style: minimal, clean, engineering catalog, technical drawing style, professional, 4K render.</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
